title: Good King Dagobert, Le Bon Roi Dagobert 1984 Coluche, Michel Serrault, Carole Bouquet, Isabella Ferrari, Karin Mai, Sabrina Siani, Pietro Torris, Moana Pozzi, Sabine Jager + Dino Risi

sources.title: Good King Dagobert, Le Bon Roi Dagobert 1984 Coluche, Michel Serrault, Carole Bouquet, Isabella Ferrari, Karin Mai, Sabrina Siani, Pietro Torris, Moana Pozzi, Sabine Jager + Dino Risi
sources.description: A French/Italian farce with a significant number of beautiful women and an almost complete lack of good looking men. In particular, Coluche, who plays the title role is not presented in a favorable fashion either physically nor morally. Perhaps a closer viewing would show some pointed barbs at royalty and the church as both of those are easy and common targets for humor. In French with English subtitles.
